img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n人地等你成個月<br />\n連拒絕都冇句比人<br />\n咁冇救啦算吧啦 <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n個個月有見面，只係佢零wtsapp我<br />\n見面問過佢其實鐘意我啲咩 佢話就腳<br />\n到最後個段wtsapp先同我講真心說話"},{"pid":"b5921ef8cfeaab177f54e4e63f3e3bf44adf6ac2","tid":175861,"uid":13374,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-27T19:15:25.000Z","msg":"其實由佢表白果刻都注定左做唔成朋友 <br />\n不過係佢表完之後一個月就搵到新仔都知你應該都冇考慮同重視個依個朋友<br />\n比著係我都心鳩淡啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"666b5d7810ef27a7437a1fb18967b70cd1f40f32","tid":175861,"uid":31238,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-27T19:15:49.000Z","msg":"幾個追求者咁威呀樓主<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  總要人地等你成個月都唔比個答覆人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"87bec77a375074b69a2ba1806644a840b000893e","tid":175861,"uid":3177,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-27T19:16:19.000Z","msg":"朋友更加咪拖泥帶水 <br />\n站係朋友立場 你搵到個鍾意嘅都會登你開心 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"65d3fbf278c67116b9aecf78c4b7f6ee2d58dcad","tid":175861,"uid":54904,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-27T19:16:53.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/88mZs08.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F88mZs08.jpg&h=d9c08edf&s={SIZE}\" /></blockquote><br />\n公開處刑<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ba0c390bf95d7def4601e856b49a457de0f2e00f","tid":175861,"uid":53836,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-27T19:18:32.000Z","msg":"屌啦，人地仲on99咁等你答覆，想比d空間你，日日都食唔安訓唔落<br />\n點知你果時已經同其他人曖昧緊，仲要一齊埋佢仲係懵盛盛，乜春都唔知<br />\n<br />\n全部都係雞<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"56bc36803d5ca9d3eff27113457409294c19dbc7","tid":175861,"uid":23613,"like":0,"